data.description: Examines core components of championships sports programs. Uses case study design to examine how leadership unfolds across multiple levels within one setting. Draws from distributed leadership analytic framework. Considers how matters such as talent, culture, commitment, leadership, intelligence, organization, resilience, teamwork, integrity, health, resources, and opportunities intersect in a successful system.
data.title: RUNNING A CHAMPIONSHIP SYSTEM: THE BADGER SPORTS LEADERSHIP ROAD COURSE
